{"tid":527591,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"高度集中　4%人掌握全球97%比特幣！ (21:37)","createTime":"2018-01-12T22:46:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-13T07:35:44.000Z","uid":17738,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"799238434f5f5ae8a81b74196ffafdbe8e783ca2","tid":527591,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T22:46:36.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=NH1cLd6b0HR8c04Itq7TQIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=5a8b7eac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】瑞士信貸的一份最新報告表示，比特幣(Bitcoin)可能又是一場由金字塔頂端1%人操控的財富遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n瑞士信貸在發送給客戶的一份關於加密貨幣和區塊鏈的報告中表示，全球97%的比特幣被4%的比特幣地址所持有。<br />\n<br />\n該行表示，財富集中在一小群地址上&mdash;&mdash;不論他們是個人還是交易所，意味遊戲中的少數關鍵玩家可以對整個比特幣市場產生巨大影響。<br />\n<br />\n這些在加密世界中被稱作持有者的人正牢牢抓住手中的比特幣。在這種情況下，這一生態系統中的財富變得非常集中。<br />\n<br />\n相比之下，根據瑞士信貸去年11月的一份分析報告，全球最富1%人口僅掌握着大約一半的財富。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20180112/20180112213737fi.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20180112%2F20180112213737fi.html&d=NH1cLd6b0HR8c04Itq7TQIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=62b83cef\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20180112/20180112213737fi.html</a>"},{"pid":"70cf0d1b955b4ca09b9ec9e0a0a9b4326b76a8c6","tid":527591,"uid":51127,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T22:48:34.000Z","msg":"跟本同老千股一樣玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eca26c2455e602dcd71da2868848452592c8c1e","tid":527591,"uid":17103,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T22:57:20.000Z","msg":"又話匿名既"},{"pid":"1c1cf6cb6980c6cfa062739543cc0212e6421d1a","tid":527591,"uid":2035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5eca26c2455e602dcd71da2868848452592c8c1e","tid":527591,"uid":17103,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T22:57:20.000Z","msg":"又話匿名既"},"